verbose_text: There was a significant increase in the mRNA expression of C-sis in the C-sis plasmid group compared with the normal control and empty plasmid groups (P < 0.01; XREF_FIG), and there was a significant increase in the protein expression of C-sis in the C-sis plasmid group compared with the normal control and empty plasmid groups (P < 0.01; XREF_FIG).
